venue.name: P.F. Chang's Restaurant inside the Natick Collection

item.description: We will be hanging out, relaxing and having drinks and appetizers/dinner. Everyone pays for their own food/drinks. Come join us!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine ('ll be wearing a bright green coat). We will be in the bar area, then move to tables. If need help finding us, please call 774 232 0000.
item.why: Join us for a fun and relaxing time and good food! Joint event with the 25+ Social Fun Meetup group.
item.name: Drinks and Dinner at P.F. Chang's at the Natick Collection
